{{> layout}}
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.css">
<div class="home-body">
    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section id="intro">
        <div class="container">
            <p>Welcome to The Scottish Pantry Network, where we connect individuals with surplus food to local food pantries, helping reduce food waste and support communities in need.</p>
            <a href="#login" class="btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <p>The Scottish Pantry Network is a community-driven initiative that aims to tackle food waste and promote sustainable living. We are proud to work with local authorities, network members, and collective pantry members to make a positive impact in our communities.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="impact">
        <h2>Our Impact</h2>
        <p class="impact-box">10 Local Authorities</p>
        <p class="impact-box">23 Network Members</p>
        <p class="impact-box">34,000 Collective Pantry Members</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Local Suppliers</h2>
        <p>We work closely with local suppliers to provide an effective alternative to help reduce food waste, which aligns with our global climate commitments.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Our Recipes</h2>
        <p>We offer an extensive selection of recipes that are regularly updated to encourage everyone to make the most of the fresh food provided through our Pantries.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Join Our Newsletter</h2>
        <p>Stay up to date with the latest information on TSPN and your local community pantry by subscribing to our newsletter.</p>
        <div class="subscribe-container">
            <form class="subscribe-box">
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                <button type="submit">Subscribe Now</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
